      "status": "Idea",
      "notes": "Sometimes I need to talk through how certain tasks need to be done and I don’t like typing them out, especially in some format of structure. I have to follow so I think it would be good to create like an AI where I can input the type of task it is and then it runs through a series of pre-trained questions and thinks critically on my answer to ask better questions to be able to develop a standardized useful SOP and then we use that SOP for all the SOP‘s in a business or at least that template so like, for example, how to schedule my travel if I had to sit down and write that out, it would be a pain in the ass for me, but I can have Claude ask me certain questions and I can just talk freely to it and then it can take useful information. Ask some additional questions as needed and keep doing that through a series of questions until it gets all the information that it needs, and then it creates the one page SOP for me. \n\nThis will be really good if we add in like a mindset and perspective on the backend of the AI that understands that I have difficulty delegating task sometimes so then it forces me questions to answer that will help someone else take that job on, so for example, I have a really hard time with if a listing needs vendors that need to go to the house and I have the notes on what needs to be done and I need to like talk to vendors in a specific way then I just take that on, but it would be really good for the AI to push me and stretch me to develop an SOP or someone can actually take this and run with it and I can delegate It. ",
